20:23.610 --> 20:26.006
- Thank you for helping me.
- Mmm-hmm.

20:26.126 --> 20:28.325
I'm guessing Aaron wasn't available.

20:28.644 --> 20:30.207
Ha-ha!

20:31.636 --> 20:34.719
So, did you hear? Ana and the baby
are moving in with me and Mike?

20:34.746 --> 20:36.018
- No.
- Yeah.

20:36.077 --> 20:38.544
I guess we're gonna move into
that three-bedroom in our building.

20:38.664 --> 20:40.643
Great.

20:40.701 --> 20:43.034
