20:50.069 --> 20:51.192
He does?

20:53.062 --> 20:54.415
What do you think?

20:54.959 --> 20:56.245
I wouldn't mind.

20:56.365 --> 20:58.449
Mike's been good to me, but...

20:59.916 --> 21:02.029
I don't know how Ty would feel about it.

21:02.149 --> 21:03.732
You know, him being a white cop and all.

21:03.799 --> 21:06.176
I thought Ty was glad that
you had Mike looking after you.

21:06.181 --> 21:07.201
Yeah, but

21:07.569 --> 21:09.673
fostering is different than adopting.

21:09.700 --> 21:12.105
I just... I'd want
him to be cool with it.

21:12.225 --> 21:14.931
If it's what you want,
then he should be.

21:15.355 --> 21:16.613
I think you should ask him.

21:16.915 --> 21:17.854
Hey.

21:18.280 --> 21:20.834
- What are you doing?
- Uh, we are taking this down.

21:20.875 --> 21:22.695
Why? The Open House is tomorrow.

21:22.709 --> 21:24.030
Yeah, that's the point.

21:24.150 --> 21:25.856
Monte doesn't think that

21:25.923 --> 21:29.685
my project is appropriate for
prospective families, so...

21:29.755 --> 21:31.944
Are you serious? That's total BS.

21:34.124 --> 21:36.299
I finally got my own room.

21:36.308 --> 21:38.699
I should've nailed
myself in the head sooner.

21:39.872 --> 21:41.306
Not funny.

21:41.917 --> 21:43.328
You know what is funny?

21:44.092 --> 21:48.933
Brandon having to
share a room with Jude.

21:49.931 --> 21:52.618
I think it's very sweet
that he gave you his room.

21:52.847 --> 21:54.933
- You might be a little grateful.
- Okay.

21:57.072 --> 21:58.955
Slow your roll there, Foster.

21:59.939 --> 22:02.735
You wanna help me with some...

22:03.283 --> 22:05.067
physical therapy?

22:06.231 --> 22:08.676
I don't know if you're up for that.

22:08.680 --> 22:11.736
Oh, no, no, no. I'm up.

