23:35.005 --> 23:36.453
Getting good grades.

23:37.223 --> 23:38.758
Uh, so,

23:39.595 --> 23:41.860
I wanted to talk to you about...

23:42.028 --> 23:44.765
- you know, my situation.
- Yeah. Yeah, me, too.

23:45.304 --> 23:48.534
