out of here in a few months."

23:48.654 --> 23:50.961
- For real?
- Told you, I've been doing good.

23:51.388 --> 23:53.904
Plus, I get these credits
that shorten my sentence

23:53.926 --> 23:55.595
for the courses I've
been taking in here.

23:55.629 --> 23:58.202
- Like what?
- I'm in firefighter training.

23:58.410 --> 24:01.663
That's got me thinking about
doing that once I get out.

24:02.146 --> 24:04.140
You know, do something to help people.

24:04.260 --> 24:07.584
Anyway, I'm gonna get a
job, as soon as I'm out.

24:07.781 --> 24:09.123
And you're gonna be 18.

24:09.145 --> 24:11.196
So you can move in with
me, just like we planned.

24:11.269 --> 24:12.938
You can go to college if you want.

24:13.253 --> 24:15.988
I'm gonna take care
of the rent, all that.

24:17.285 --> 24:18.769
Yeah, yeah. That all...

24:18.983 --> 24:20.477
That sounds good, man.

24:24.258 --> 24:25.758
Oh. Hey.

24:25.878 --> 24:27.152
Hey.

24:30.247 --> 24:31.314
I'm sorry.

24:33.797 --> 24:35.404
How, uh...

24:36.636 --> 24:39.036
- How're you feeling?
- I'm okay.

24:39.071 --> 24:40.434
Yeah, you sure?

24:40.773 --> 24:41.973
Yeah.

24:43.876 --> 24:46.524
Your brother wants to...

24:46.535 --> 24:47.513
What?

24:48.581 --> 24:49.693
Oh.

24:49.813 --> 24:52.283
- Sorry.
- No.

24:52.317 --> 24:54.732
I told him he's
probably not well enough.

24:54.733 --> 24:55.817
Right.

24:56.328 --> 24:59.069
And I'm not...

24:59.980 --> 25:01.491
No, of course.

25:03.042 --> 25:04.628
Sorry, it's just that...

25:05.642 --> 25:07.272
nobody else knows.

25:07.845 --> 25:09.986
Uh, well, that's okay.

25:10.031 --> 25:11.496
You know, um...

25:11.616 --> 25:15.754
I'm not exactly, like...

25:16.007 --> 25:18.608
qualified or anything, but...

25:19.855 --> 25:21.754
if you ever...

25:21.956 --> 25:25.052
you know, need to talk about
it or anything, I'm always...

25:25.085 --> 25:27.243
- Thanks.
- Yeah.

25:30.833 --> 25:32.209
Jesus.

25:34.434 --> 25:36.243
_

